theorem Topology.P3_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    Topology.P3 (A := interior A) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P3]
  intro x hx
  have h_subset : interior A ⊆ interior (closure (interior A)) :=
    interior_mono (Set.subset_closure : interior A ⊆ closure (interior A))
  exact h_subset hx

theorem Topology.P3_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    Topology.P3 (A := interior A) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P3]
  intro x hx
  have h_sub : interior A ⊆ interior (closure (interior A)) :=
    interior_mono (subset_closure : interior A ⊆ closure (interior A))
  exact h_sub hx

theorem Topology.P3_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    Topology.P3 (A := interior A) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P3]
  intro x hx
  have h : interior A ⊆ interior (closure (interior A)) :=
    interior_mono (Set.subset_closure (s := interior A))
  exact h hx

theorem subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    A ⊆ closure A :=
  Set.subset_closure

theorem Topology.P1_union {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (hA : Topology.P1 (A := A)) (hB : Topology.P1 (A := B)) :
    Topology.P1 (A := A ∪ B) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P1] at *
  intro x hx_union
  cases hx_union with
  | inl hxA =>
      have hx_closureA : x ∈ closure (interior A) := hA hxA
      have h_subset : interior A ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) :=
        interior_mono (Set.subset_union_left A B)
      have h_closure_subset : closure (interior A) ⊆ closure (interior (A ∪ B)) :=
        closure_mono h_subset
      exact h_closure_subset hx_closureA
  | inr hxB =>
      have hx_closureB : x ∈ closure (interior B) := hB hxB
      have h_subset : interior B ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) :=
        interior_mono (Set.subset_union_right A B)
      have h_closure_subset : closure (interior B) ⊆ closure (interior (A ∪ B)) :=
        closure_mono h_subset
      exact h_closure_subset hx_closureB

theorem Topology.subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    A ⊆ closure A := by
  exact Set.subset_closure
